item.description: The weather is warming up and it is time to gear up for beach volleyball. Let's go to the Old Salt to have fun and catch up. Afterwards we will go from there. Returning volleyball players and new volleyball players are welcome. Sorry this is so last minute. If you do not make it, then I will update about volleyball you on facebook or via email. Hope to see you all there.
item.how_to_find_us: We will be in the bar area....we will look for ya if you are new.
